<section class="features section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="features-header">
      <p class="eyebrow">WHEN YOU WANT THE BEST</p>
      <h2>Criminal Lawyer Springfield MO</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>COURTROOM FOCUSED</h3>
        <p>Thomas Carver is a trial lawyer. He has spent more than 45 years in courtrooms across Missouri and the United States, defending people accused of serious crimes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>UNRIVALED EXPERIENCE</h3>
        <p>With more than 300 federal cases and thousands of state cases handled, our experience is unmatched in the Springfield area.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>RECOGNIZED EXCELLENCE</h3>
        <p>A five-time Lawyer of the Year and a Super Lawyer for 15 consecutive years, Thomas Carver is recognized by his peers as one of the best.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section { padding: 6rem 0; }
  .features-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  .eyebrow {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .features-header h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: #f9f9f9;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    border-top: 4px solid var(--color-accent);
    transition: transform 0.3s;
  }
  .feature-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    color: var(--color-body-text);
  }
</style>
